'''Permaculture Forums''' at [http://www.permies.com/ www.permies.com] is an [[online community]] discussing all aspects of [[permaculture]]. It has more than 16,000 members who have made more than 37,000 posts on almost 4000 topics.<ref>Statistics given above the list of forums at http://www.permies.com/permaculture-forums</ref>

The '''Permaculture subreddit''' [http://www.reddit.com/r/Permaculture] is a small, but active community.

== Permaculture Forums on Appropedia ==

Permaculture Forums members who may wish to share a page with their community, in a public way, are free to use [[Appropedia]]. Pages specifically related to the PF community may be made subpages of this one, using a slash "/". E.g. if you wanted to share links related to a forum discussion on [[composting]], you could start the page [[Permaculture Forums/composting]] or [[Permaculture Forums/composting links]].

